'''信德'''（Sindh；[[信德語|信德語]]：سنڌ；[[烏爾都語|烏爾都語]]：سندھ；[[羅馬化|羅馬化]]拼寫曾作Sind）是[[巴基斯坦行政區劃|巴基斯坦的四個省]]之一。信德省位於該國東南部地區，是巴基斯坦總面積第三大省，人口僅次於[[旁遮普省|旁遮普省]]的第二大省。它分別與北部的巴基斯坦[[俾路支省|俾路支省]]和旁遮普省以及東部的印度[[古吉拉特邦|古吉拉特邦]]和[[拉賈斯坦邦|拉賈斯坦邦]]接壤；它的南面以[[阿拉伯海|阿拉伯海]]為界。信德省的景觀主要由[[印度河|印度河]]兩側的[[沖積平原|沖積平原]]、該省東部與印度接壤的[[塔爾沙漠|塔爾沙漠]]和該省西部的[[基爾塔爾山脈|基爾塔爾山脈]]組成。

信德省的經濟是巴基斯坦僅次於旁遮普省的第二大經濟體；其省會[[卡拉奇|卡拉奇]]是該國人口最多的城市，也是其主要金融中心。信德省是巴基斯坦大部分[[工業|工業]]機構的所在地，並擁有該國兩個最繁忙的商業海港：[[卡西姆港|卡西姆港]]和[[卡拉奇港|卡拉奇港]]。信德省的其餘地區以[[農業|農業]]為基礎，為該國其他地區生產[[水果|水果]]、[[日用品|日用品]]和[[蔬菜|蔬菜]]。<ref name="The Nation, 2014">{{cite news|last1=Staff reporter|title=Sindh must exploit potential for fruit production|url=http://nation.com.pk/business/09-Mar-2014/sindh-must-exploit-potential-for-fruit-production|access-date=29 May 2015|agency=The Nation|publisher=The Nation, 2014|date=9 March 2014|archive-date=2017-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171002215717/http://nation.com.pk/business/09-Mar-2014/sindh-must-exploit-potential-for-fruit-production|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="SALU Press">{{cite journal|title=Dates in Sindh|url=https://www.academia.edu/1934949|first1=Ghulam Sarwar|last2=Saud|first2=Adila A.|journal=Proceedings of the International Dates Seminar|publisher=SALU Press|last1=Markhand|access-date=29 May 2015|archive-date=2022-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220301053313/https://www.academia.edu/1934949|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Dawn News,2007">{{cite news|last1=Editorial|title=How to grow Bananas|url=http://www.dawn.com/news/264225/how-to-grow-bananas|access-date=29 May 2015|agency=Dawn News|publisher=Dawn News, 2007|date=3 September 2007|archive-date=2022-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220310044045/https://www.dawn.com/news/264225/how-to-grow-bananas|dead-url=no}}</ref>

信德有時被稱為 Bab-ul Islam（譯作“伊斯蘭之門”），因為它是[[印度次大陸|印度次大陸]]最早受伊斯蘭政權統治的地區之一。現代省份的部分地區在早期[[穆斯林的征服|穆斯林征服]]期間受到拉什頓軍隊（英語：Rashidun army，即[[正統哈里發時期|正統哈里發]]政權當時的核心武裝力量）的[[穆斯林征服印度次大陸|間歇性襲擊]]，但該地區直到 712 年由[[穆罕默德·伊本·卡西木|穆罕默德·伊本·卡西姆]]領導的[[倭瑪亞王朝|倭馬亞哈里發]]統治下發生阿拉伯入侵信德後，才落入穆斯林政權的統治。<ref>{{Cite book|last=Quddus|first=Syed Abdul|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Q_dtAAAAMAAJ&q=babul+islam+sindh|title=Sindh, the Land of Indus Civilisation|date=1992|publisher=Royal Book Company|isbn=978-969-407-131-2|language=en|access-date=2022-02-10|archive-date=2022-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220301053319/https://books.google.com/books?id=Q_dtAAAAMAAJ&q=babul+islam+sindh|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=uE26AAAAIAAJ&q=babul+islam+sindh+qasim|title=JPRS Report: Near East & South Asia|date=1992|publisher=Foreign Broadcast Information Service|language=en|access-date=2022-02-10|archive-date=2022-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220301053323/https://books.google.com/books?id=uE26AAAAIAAJ&q=babul+islam+sindh+qasim|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[信德族|信德族]]是該省最大的群體；信德省也是絕大多數[[穆哈吉爾人|穆哈吉爾人]]（烏爾都語：مہاجر，拼寫作Mahajir或Mahajir、Mohajir等，字面意思是“移民”）的居住地，這是一個多民族的印度穆斯林群體，他們在 1947 年[[印巴分治|英屬印度分治]]後遷移到該地區。該省以其受[[蘇菲派|蘇菲派]]強烈影響的獨特文化聞名，蘇菲派是當地[[印度教|印度教]]徒和[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]身份認同的共同重要標誌。<ref name="WakabayashiKothari2009">{{cite book|author1=Judy Wakabayashi|author2=Rita Kothari|title=Decentering Translation Studies: India and Beyond|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=viRCNDBYd4kC&pg=PT132|year=2009|publisher=John Benjamins Publishing|isbn=978-90-272-2430-9|pages=132–|access-date=2022-02-10|archive-date=2022-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220301053329/https://books.google.com/books?id=viRCNDBYd4kC&pg=PT132|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

信德省以其在[[印度河流域文明|印度河流域文明]]時期的青銅時代的歷史而聞名，並且是聯合國教科文組織指定的兩個世界遺產地的所在地：馬克利墓地（英語：Makli Necropolis，世界當今最大的[[大墓地|大墓地]]之一，約有50至100萬座<ref name="arch">{{cite web|title=Makli Hill|url=https://archnet.org/sites/1751|access-date=17 July 2017|website=ArchNet|publisher=Aga Khan Trust for Culture and the Massachusetts Institute of Technology (MIT)|archive-date=2019-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190410050035/https://archnet.org/sites/1751|dead-url=no}}</ref>建立於約400年期間的墳墓<ref name="UNESCO">{{cite web|title=Historical Monuments at Makli, Thatta|url=https://whc.unesco.org/en/list/143|access-date=17 July 2017|publisher=UNESCO|archive-date=2012-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120808063056/http://whc.unesco.org/en/list/143/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以數座獻給皇室、蘇菲派重要人物、學者的紀念物為特色，被認定是信德地區文明14至18世紀發展的重要遺跡<ref>[https://whc.unesco.org/en/list/143 Historical Monuments at Makli, Thatta] {{Wayback|url=https://whc.unesco.org/en/list/143 |date=20120808063056 }} UNESCO World Heritage Centre. Retrieved 10 February 2011</ref>）和[[摩亨佐達羅|摩亨佐達羅]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Properties inscribed on the World Heritage List (Pakistan)|url=https://whc.unesco.org/en/statesparties/pk|access-date=14 July 2016|website=UNESCO|publisher=UNESCO|archive-date=2016-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160704110025/https://whc.unesco.org/en/statesparties/pk|dead-url=no}}</ref>

該省的（官方）象徵動物為信德羱羊（Sindh ibex）<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=‘Our Sindhi symbols – ibex, black partridge’ {{!}} Pakistan Today|url=https://archive.pakistantoday.com.pk/2011/12/14/%e2%80%98our-sindhi-symbols-%e2%80%93-ibex-black-partridge%e2%80%99/|access-date=2022-02-10|last=Hussain|language=en-GB|archive-date=2022-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220301053423/https://archive.pakistantoday.com.pk/2011/12/14/%E2%80%98our-sindhi-symbols-%E2%80%93-ibex-black-partridge%E2%80%99/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，象徵鳥類為[[黑鶉|黑鶉]]<ref name=":0" />，象徵樹種為[[印度苦楝樹|印度苦楝樹]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Govt declares Neem `provincial tree`|url=http://beta.dawn.com/news/978487/govt-declares-neem-provincial-tree|access-date=2022-02-10|date=2010-04-15|work=DAWN.COM|language=en}}</ref>。以該地區名稱命名之物種有信德羱羊及[[信德麻雀|信德麻雀]]等。

== 詞源 ==
公元前 325 年在[[亞歷山大大帝|亞歷山大大帝]]的指揮下征服信德的[[希臘人|希臘人]]將[[印度河|印度河]]（英語：Indus River）稱為 Indós，現代之Indus稱呼由此衍生。 古代[[伊朗人|伊朗人]]把印度河以東的一切都稱為hind（現代羅馬化拼寫形式）。<ref name="Now or Never">{{cite web|title=Now or Never. Are we to live or perish forever?|url=http://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Now_or_Never;_Are_We_to_Live_or_Perish_Forever%3F|author=Choudhary Rahmat Ali|date=28 January 1933|access-date=2022-02-10|archive-date=2008-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080630210551/http://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Now_or_Never;_Are_We_to_Live_or_Perish_Forever|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Ikram1995">{{cite book|author=S. M. Ikram|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=7q9EubOYZmwC&pg=PA177|title=Indian Muslims and partition of India|date=1 January 1995|publisher=Atlantic Publishers & Dist|isbn=978-81-7156-374-6|pages=177–|author-link=S. M. Ikram|access-date=23 December 2011|archive-date=2022-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220301053442/https://books.google.com/books?id=7q9EubOYZmwC&pg=PA177|dead-url=no}}</ref> Sindh 一詞是[[梵語|梵語]] Sindhu 的[[波斯語|波斯語]][[派生詞|派生詞]]，意思是“河流”—指印度河。{{sfn|Phiroze Vasunia|2013|p=6}}

Franklin Southworth 認為 Sindhu 這個名字又來源於 Cintu，這是一個[[德拉威語|德拉威語]]中[[棗椰樹|棗椰樹]]的意思，一種在當地常見的樹。<ref>Southworth, Franklin. [https://www.academia.edu/7336735/The_Reconstruction_of_Prehistoric_South_Asian_Language_Contact The Reconstruction of Prehistoric South Asian Language Contact] {{Wayback|url=https://www.academia.edu/7336735/The_Reconstruction_of_Prehistoric_South_Asian_Language_Contact |date=20220301053430 }} (1990) p. 228</ref><ref>Burrow, T. [https://dsalsrv04.uchicago.edu/cgi-bin/app/burrow_query.py?qs=īntu&searchhws=yes Dravidian Etymology Dictionary] {{Wayback|url=https://dsalsrv04.uchicago.edu/cgi-bin/app/burrow_query.py?qs=%C4%ABntu&searchhws=yes |date=20210301115537 }} p. 227</ref>

之前的拼寫形式“Sind”（來自[[波斯字母系統|波斯阿拉伯]]詞彙سند）在 1988 年因當地[[議會|議會]]通過的一項修正法案而終止。<ref>{{cite news|title=Sindh, not Sind|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/506227/sind-not-sindh/|access-date=16 October 2015|work=[[The_Express_Tribune|The Express Tribune]]|publisher=Web Desk|date=12 February 2013|archive-date=2022-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220301053459/https://tribune.com.pk/story/506227/sind-not-sindh|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 行政区划 ==
信德省辖有29个县。分别为[[巴丁县|巴丁县]]、[[达杜县|达杜县]]、[[海德拉巴县|海德拉巴县]]等。

